  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-04 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains a subtle model-version drift: the primary ValidationResult was generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, whereas the UnitOfAssurance records currentModelVersion as 2026-q1-build-7 (the released patch). The simulation team noted the RC2 and release builds are 'effectively the same' and did not re-run validation under the released version.",
